    "Name": "Ranger RGR-2X",
    "Details": "The RGR-2X trades the 1X's Light PPCs and six heat sinks for a left-arm Ultra AC/10 fed by two tons of CASE-protected ammunition, producing significantly heavier hitting power at the cost of logistical independence. Two ER Medium Lasers, a Medium Pulse Laser, and two ER Small Lasers are retained from the original configuration. Endo Steel construction and an additional ton of armor offset the weight investment in the ballistic system. This proved to be the most commercially successful Ranger variant.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Energy</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
    "Icon": "NEEDS_ICON"
